@index "CanDo_MasterIndex"

@node "CanDo_Card_Editor" "CanDo's Card Editor"
@toc "CanDo_Main"
   This requester allows you to change the name and scripts of the current
card.  You can define up to five different scripts for each card.
   
   @{fg highlight}Objects...@{fg text}

      BeforeAttachment
         Executed before this card's window and objects attach.
      AfterAttachment
         Executed after this card's window and objects attach.
      BeforeDetachment
         Executed before card shuts down.  This could be caused
         by a card transition or the deck shutting down.
      
   @{fg highlight}Message...@{fg text}

      From a Sub-Deck
         Executed when one of the sub-deck's scripts of this card
         performs a @{" SendToParentDeck " link "CanDo_SendToParentDeck"} command.
      From Parent-Deck
         Executed when one of the parent-deck's scripts of this card
         performs a @{" SendToSubDeck " link "CanDo_SendToSubDeck"} command.
         
   You can copy whole cards, including all their windows and objects, via
the @{" Copy/Paste " link "CanDo_MPCopyPaste"} system available via the MainPanel.

@endnode

